
### Get records overview (KPI metrics)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/dashboard/records/overview

### Get records breakdown by status
GET http://localhost:5000/api/dashboard/records/by-status

### Get records breakdown by document type
GET http://localhost:5000/api/dashboard/records/by-document-type

### Get records breakdown by sponsor
GET http://localhost:5000/api/dashboard/records/by-sponsor

### Get top downloaded records (with limit parameter)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/dashboard/records/top-downloaded?limit=10

### Get records created timeline (by month)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/dashboard/records/timeline/created

### Get records issued timeline (by month)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/dashboard/records/timeline/issued

### Get records date range distribution (7, 30, 90 days)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/dashboard/records/date-range-distribution

